    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/59aa1a648757db46abb3d535524b53fb.avif?t=1771231860\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>联邦政府正在呼吁你加入为人类而战的行列。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>这就是《星河战队: 终焉虫潮》！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿拉奇虫的威胁已经从他们的母星克兰达夫星扩散，入侵银河中人类的领土。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将亲自参与及引领人类作出崇高努力，一起保护银河系。驾驭多样而独特的机动步兵武器，通过萨曼莎·迪兹（萨米）少校的视角，焚烧、肢解并削弱亚瑞克尼虫的威胁，体验第一人称、高强度的战争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏将让你沉浸于有史以来最真实的战争描绘中！我们的游戏与理论部门打造了一个真实的復古第一人称射击体验，包括来自如强尼·瑞克将军般的联邦传奇提供的高品质全动态影像广播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/597696fb06a791582895e748884b2472.avif?t=1771231860\" width=1200 height=400 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">造访泽格玛海滩。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到泽格玛海滩，银河系中最奢华的度假胜地之一！探索其美丽的海滩、令人屏息的风景和享誉盛名的度假村。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢联邦，享受一次免费的瑰丽之旅！你将有机会深入体验这场实战：刀锋行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/17e78bb88ca483cd81de4c24ad5b5475.poster.avif?t=1771231860\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/17e78bb88ca483cd81de4c24ad5b5475.webm?t=1771231860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/17e78bb88ca483cd81de4c24ad5b5475.mp4?t=1771231860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">虫子绝不会让你休息！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别浪费时间了，士兵！我们有工作要做。正如我们所说，虫族正在袭击泽格玛海滩的怡人海岸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些敌人凶残而且拥有自己的技能。敏捷、飞行、喷发如箭，穿刺如针：这麽多不同类型的虫子在这片区域内，威胁无处不在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清理原始海滩，消灭虫子的滋生，保卫军事哨站，为增援部队铺平道路，协助疏散伤者和平民。你可以选择何时及如何处理每个目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/3883b925b39513e9e08bdec8255b6413.poster.avif?t=1771231860\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/3883b925b39513e9e08bdec8255b6413.webm?t=1771231860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/3883b925b39513e9e08bdec8255b6413.mp4?t=1771231860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">不惜一切手段奋战到底</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >联邦认可你对这份使命的奉献，士兵。你可以从任务简报内的四个选项中选择级别和难度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这次任务中，你可以依靠其他机动步兵的支援以及联邦提供的最佳反虫武器和装备。在战场上可以拾取不同的步枪，每把步枪都具有其独特的射程、弹药和射速。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砲塔和补给箱被设置在战场中的战略位置。多亏了联邦有力的军事训练，萨米还可以使用完整的技能库，例如手榴弹、信号弹或一把可靠的靴刀来消灭那些令人厌恶的虫子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/cd1f59f0228d6156e41aa5782e6f9e72.poster.avif?t=1771231860\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/cd1f59f0228d6156e41aa5782e6f9e72.webm?t=1771231860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4307720/extras/cd1f59f0228d6156e41aa5782e6f9e72.mp4?t=1771231860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">你在尽自己的一份力吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">立即在星河战队: 终焉虫潮中报名加入机动部队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>记得－服役保证公民身份</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
